('6','1','what\'s Guiding You','What is Guiding You and what can I do at Guiding You','guide,activity,guiding you,travel,optional tour','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">What’s Guiding You</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/whats_guiding_you_1_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"what\'s guiding you\" width=\"1170\" height=\"700\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_space_1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<p>“Let’s make friend while traveling around the world! ”<br /><br /> Way you enjoy your travel would easily gets changed depend on you can find right guide who already have experienced. <br /><br /> Thus “Guiding you” would like to be the bridge to connect the travelers around the world, through helping to find the right guide at different countries, interpreter, also to book interesting activities.<br /><br /> Anyone including the enterprise can register activities and be a guide, because you know the most out of it!<br /> Where would you like to take the tourists to your favorite spots? And provide great activities that hidden in the guidebooks for new experiences? <br /><br /><br /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/whats_guiding_you_2_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/whats_guiding_you_3_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/whats_guiding_you_4_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/whats_guiding_you_5_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_space_1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<p>Take them to fun events such as BBQ in great nature, authentic traditional cousin seminar, secret scuba diving spot, restraints (Ramen) where keeping their taste real or the new night clubbing tour!!!! <br /><br /> It is such an honorable thing that if tourist enjoy and be happy for your guide and culture, and one day if they come back to your city and country.<br /> Of course broad sightseeing activity is more than welcoming too! <br /> Your idea is the one makes the best experience!</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','whats-guiding-you'),
('6','2','Guiding you とは?','Guiding you（ガイディングユー）とは何か？何ができるのか？','ガイディングユー,ガイド,アクティビティ,オプショナルツアー','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">世界中の旅先で友達を作ろう</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/whats_guiding_you_1_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"what\'s guiding you\" width=\"1170\" height=\"700\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<p>旅先で現地に知り合い或はガイドがいるかいないかで楽しみ方が大きく変わりますよね！<br /><br /> 観光客はこのGuiding Youのプラットフォームを通じて、旅行先のガイドを探したり、通訳を探したり、或は他では無い面白いアクティビティを予約をしたりと、旅先で人と人を繋げるプラットフォームでありたい！<br /> それがGuiding Youのコンセプトです。<br /><br /> 楽しい経験を提供するのは現地にいる個人や企業です！誰でもガイドやアクティビティに登録する事が出来ます。<br /><br /> ガイドブックには載っていない、アナタのお気に入りのスポットや楽しいアクティビティにゲストを連れて行ってみるの如何ですか？<br /><br /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/whats_guiding_you_2_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/whats_guiding_you_3_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/whats_guiding_you_4_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/whats_guiding_you_5_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>大自然でBBQのイベント</li>\n<li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>地元伝統料理教室</li>\n<li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>秘密のダイビングスポット</li>\n<li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>本当に美味しいレストラン案内</li>\n</ul><p>或はゲストが知らない最新のナイトクラブツアーでも良いですよね？<br /> ゲストにアナタの国や町を好きになってもらい、そしてもう一度戻ってくるようにもてなしましょう。<br /><br /> 当然一般的な観光コースツアーやアクティビティでもOK、最高な経験を提供するのはアナタのアイデア次第です。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','whats-guiding-you'),
