('7','1','How to enjoy at Guiding You','How can to enjoy at Guiding You','guiding you,enjoy,guide,actvity,travel,optional tour','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">How to enjoy the “Guiding you”</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/enjoy_1_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"what\'s guiding you\" width=\"1170\" height=\"700\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><br /><h2>There are various ways to enjoy your traveling</h2>\n<br /><p><br /> Going with friends, family, or try going other place alone! How you are going to enjoy your trip will definitely changes whether you have a guide or not at the spot you are going to travel. <br /><br /></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/enjoy_2_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\n<br /><p><br /> It is really fun to discover new places that is not shown on the guidebook but “Guiding you”, For example, you can find a guide who has same kind of hobby like you and dedicate your time with your guide for hobby. <br /> Also you can look at review and decide, of course you can join activity that you are interested. <br /> Why don\'t you be a friend with a guide? So next time you come, it will be more exciting trip!<br /> If you are bored with normal sightseeing tour, you can have a fantastic time with “Guiding you”!!</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','enjoy'),
('7','2','Guiding you の楽しみ方','Guiding You（ガイディングユー）の楽しみ方','ガイド,アクティビティ,旅行,オプショナルツアー,楽しみ方','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">Guiding you の楽しみ方</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/enjoy_1_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"what\'s guiding you\" width=\"1170\" height=\"700\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><br /><h2>楽しみ方は色々</h2>\n<br /><p><br /> 一人旅行、家族旅行、友人との旅行 <br /><br /> どんな旅行でも現地にガイドがいるといないとで楽しみ方が変わりますよね！ <br /><br /> Guiding youでガイドブックに載ってない楽しみを発掘するのも楽しいでよ <br /><br /> 同じような趣味を持ったガイドを見つけて趣味に没頭する旅行でもいいかも 或はレビューを見て決めるのも一つの手です。<br /><br /></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/enjoy_2_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\n<br /><p><br /> 当然興味あるアクティビティに参加するのもよし！ <br /><br /> 案内してもらったガイドと友達になれば、次回又くる時には更に楽しさが増しますね。 <br /><br /> ありきたりな観光ツアーでは物足りない方ならGuiding youできっと楽しいひと時を過ごす事ができます。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','enjoy'),
