('10','1','how to success as guide','Key point to be successful  guide at Guiding You','guide,success,activity,travel,professional','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">How to success</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_1_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"what\'s guiding you\" width=\"1170\" height=\"700\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<p><br /><br /> There are 10 important points that you should care about, in order to get many reservations from guest when you register activity and guide.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>1.Consider, what is guest is looking for.<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_2_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>To consider what the guest whom going to abroad or domestic, are looking for. And what you can provide.<br /><br /> To provide the fun time to guest is your important roll here, therefore taking the guest to popular sightseeing spots is one of option, also this is the case to take the guest to the place where only local people knows and join their events.<br /> Or you of course can plan an event and register as activity.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>2.Create the content of activity or guide politely.<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_3_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>To input the information of activity and content of guide precisely is must, in order to get the question or reservation. <br /> Contents of activity, price, starting time, how long it’d take, warning, additional price, what kind of transportation will be using.<br /> And the most important thing is the picture. <br /> Post many pictures that relating to the guiding tour and activities, and picture of guide him/herself. <br /><br /> Guide can also register multiple activities and guide option. You can register shorten one by the deferent time program. <br /><br /> Please write in right language for guest who you want to welcome, since there are many foreigners watching.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>3.Set the price range that is competitive.<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_4_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>Set the price for each single person. <br /> Set the discount price for the guest in order to get the guide, also if you have already provided the activity as individual or as the company, you can set the price as it is. <br /><br /> It is recommended to set the price range affordable for the guest. <br /> Also this is a suggestion from “Guiding you” that we think the number of reservation will increase if the guest has the child and make the price free for the child.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>4.Reply quickly for the guest<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_5_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>It is possible to get questioning before the reservation, it is recommended to reply the question as soon as possible to get the reservation. <br /> Please tell requirement for the activity and contact information, in order to get rid of worry after the reservation. (Please tell the guest to contact at the message box at the site, in the case you do not want to tell your privacy information)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>5.Privacy Protection<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_6_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>Please use the message box on the administration of the site to exchange the information with the guest before the reservation.<br /> Do not show your phone number/E-mail Address/living Address, in order to protect own privacy information.<br /> To inform your personal information is should be told after reservation is made. <br /> It is ok to not inform your actual contact, and continuing exchanging the information in the message box at the website of “Guiding you”. <br /> Your privacy information will not be shown on the content of guide either activity’s information. (Address will be shown until “City”)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>6.Response as soon as possible when you get a contact for reservation.<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_7_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>Reply the message to the guest as soon as possible when the guest tries to contact You.<br /> Please reply the message as soon as possible, once you receive the notice of reservation mail from “Guiding you”, because the guest might need to make reservation on the spot. <br /><br /> Please include the content below for the replying.<br /><br /> ・　the date and time for the activity or guide<br /> ・　Meeting place and time<br /> ・　Attention for the activity or guide<br /> ・　Your emergency contact, if you have one. (If you have not, use message box)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>7.Take a responsibility as a guide<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_8_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>You are the guide to treat the guest nicely. <br /> It is such a nice experience to be loved your country and culture! Please utilize “Guiding you” to be friends with the guest around the world and treat them with love. <br /><br /> Please avoid canceling the activity and guide unless an emergency. <br /> Contact us and guest as soon as possible if the case happens, it is likely to occur a penalty for breach of contract depend on the content.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>8.Payment<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_9_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>Once the guest make a reservation, “Guiding you” receives the payment by credit card (PayPal).<br /> The payment will transfer to PayPal account; the guide must establish a PayPal account. (Link to Pay Pal)<br /> The payment will be transferred within2-3 days after the enforcement of the guide or activity.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>9.Ask for a review<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_10_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>Please ask for a review after treating your guest about your guide/activity.<br /> Other guests will refer that review</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>10.Write down your guide on the blog.<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_11_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>It is possible to be interested by the guest if you write down your content of guide and activity on the guide blog through administration screen. <br /> Post some pictures that you are having fun time with other guests.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','how-to-success'),
('10','2','成功するポイント','Guiding You（ガイディングユー）で成功するポイントの説明','ガイディングユー,成功,アクティビティ,ガイド,プロ,旅行','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">成功のポイント</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_1_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"what\'s guiding you\" width=\"1170\" height=\"700\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<p><br /><br /> ゲストの予約を沢山とるには注意するポイントがあります</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>1.ゲストは何を求めているかを考える<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_2_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>海外或は国内から観光に出かけるゲストは、その現地で何を求めているのか<br /> そしてアナタが何を提供出来るのかを考える必要があります<br /><br /> 一般的な観光コースはもちろんの事、それ以外にゲストはもっと現地の人が楽しんでいる場所に行きたい場合もありますよ<br /><br /> 現地のイベントに参加するのも楽しいと思います、或はあなたがイベントを企画してアクティビティとして登録してもOKです<br /><br /> ゲストに楽しい時間を提供するのがガイドの役目です</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>2.ガイドorアクティビティの内容を丁寧に作ろう<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_3_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>ゲストにアナタが登録したガイド内容やアクティビティ内容に興味を持たせ、問い合わせや予約を得る為には情報を正確に登録しなければなりません<br /><br /> ガイドやアクティビティの内容、金額、スタート時間や所用時間等、注意事項、オプションでかかる料金、移動する場合その手段、そして一番重要なのは写真です<br /><br /> ガイド本人の写真とガイドツアーやアクティビティに関連する写真を沢山載せましょう<br /><br /> ガイドは複数のガイドメニューやアクティビティーメニューを登録する事ができます<br /> 同じガイド内容でも、所用時間の違いで短いコースをつのメニューとして登録して時間が長いコースをもう一つのメニューとして登録する事ができます<br /><br /> 海外の方が見ているので、なるべく英語やその他アナタが迎え入れたいゲストが分かる言語で内容を記入しましょう</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>3.競争力ある金額の設定<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_4_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>１人あたりの金額を設定しましょう<br /> 既にアクティビティを観光客に提供している個人や企業は、その金額で設定するか、或は競争力を高める為にディスカウントした金額で登録しましょう<br /><br /> ガイドツアーの方はゲストが気軽に支払える金額に設定する事をおすすめします、更にはGuiding youからのご提案ですが、お子様のいるゲストは是非お子様を無料にして頂いたら予約が増えると思います</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>4.ゲストへのスピーディーな返信<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_5_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>予約の前にゲストから問い合わせの連絡がくる場合があります<br /> その問い合わせにはスピーディーに返信して予約へつなげましょう <br /><br /> 予約後もゲストの不安を取り除く為に、必要事項や連絡先をお伝え下さい <br /><br /> ガイドがご自分のプライバシーを告げたくない場合、引き続きサイト内のメッセージボックスで連絡を取るようにゲストのお伝え下さい</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>5.プライバシーの保護<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_6_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>予約前のゲストとのやり取りは管理画面のメッセージボックスを使ってください<br /><br /> ご自分のプライバシー保護の為に電話番号/メールアドレス/住所は掲載しないでください<br /><br /> 実際の連絡先をゲストにつたえるのは予約が確定してからにしてください <br /><br /> もちろん実際のあなたの連絡先を伝えないで、guiding youのメッセージボックスで引き続き連絡を取り合う事も出来ます<br /><br /> アナタが掲載したガイド内容やアクティビティ情報にもアナタのプライバシー情報は掲載されません住所はCityまでしか表示しません</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>6.予約がきたらすぐ連絡<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_7_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>ゲストから予約がきたらなるべく早く返信をしてください<br /><br /> ゲストは現地で予約を入れる場合が有る為、Guiding youから予約メールの通知を受け取ってからなるべく早めに返事をしてください<br /><br /> 返事する内容は以下の内容を含めて下さい<br /><br /> ・　サービスを実行する日時と時間を明記<br /> ・　待ち合わせの場所と時間<br /> ・　注意事項<br /> ・　アナタの緊急連絡先（無ければメッセージボックスで連絡と明記）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>7.ガイドとしての責任をまっとうする<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_8_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>ゲストはガイドのアナタが頼りです、ゲストに素敵なおもてなしをして、アナタの国や地域を好きになってもらいましょう<br /><br /> 世界中で友達をつくる事が出来たら素敵ですよねGuiding youを使ってゲストと友達になって、ゲストをもてなしてください<br /><br /> 尚、よほどの事が無い限り、ガイドやアクティビティのキャンセルは控えて下さい<br /> キャンセルが発生する場合は直にゲストと当社に連絡をください、内容によっては違約金が発生します</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>8.入金<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_9_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>ゲストが予約した時点でguiding youが代金をクレジットカードpaypalで受け取っています<br /> 代金のお振込はガイドのpaypal口座にされますので、ガイドは必ず<a href=\"http://paypal.com/\">paypal</a>口座を作りましょう<br /><br /> ガイド実施日程から3営業日以内に振り込まれます</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>9.レビューを依頼する<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_10_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>ゲストをもてなした後に、必ずゲストにアナタのガイド或はアクティビティにレビューを書くように依頼して下さい<br /><br /> 他のゲストがそのレビューを参考にしています</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<h2>10.ガイドブログを書く<br /><br /><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/success_11_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /></h2>\n<br /><p>管理画面からガイドブログを書く事で、ゲストはよりアナタのガイド内容やアクティビティに興味をもつかもしれません<br /><br /> 他のゲストとの楽しい時間や写真を載せてアピールしましょう</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','how-to-success'),
