('13','1','Reason to be guide at Guiding You','Reason and benefits to be a guide at Guiding You','benefit,reason,guide,activity,travel','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">Why should I be a guide?</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_1_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"what\'s guiding you\" width=\"1170\" height=\"700\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<p><br /><br /> What is the reason to be a guide at “Guiding You”?<br /><br /><br /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>You can produce benefits by what you love to do while free time</li>\n</ul><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_2_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /><p>you can draw the income by guiding tourists around the world by utilizing your language skill, knowledge, and hobby.<br /><br /> If you are already guide or interrupter, you can easily attract customer from around the world by posting advertisement through providing the activities.</p>\n<hr /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>You can be friends through sharing the how wonderful your culture is!</li>\n</ul><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_3_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /><p>This is great opportunity for you to tell how wonderful your country is!<br /><br /><br /> This is also great opportunity to make friends around the world!<br /><br /></p>\n<hr /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_space_1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>It is free to publish!</li>\n</ul><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_4_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /><p>To publish your guide and activity on “Guiding You” is free.</p>\n<hr /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_space_1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>Personal Information is guarded safely</li>\n</ul><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_5_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /><p>You are address will not be shown on the site.<br /><br /> Communication with the guest will be interchanged within the “Guiding you”s message box.</p>\n<hr /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_space_1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>You can decide the time and price range!</li>\n</ul><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_6_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /><p>You can set the price range by yourself!<br /><br /> Also you can set your date and time depend on your schedule!</p>\n<hr /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_space_1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>Commission fee is 13.5%</li>\n</ul><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_7_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /><p>Once reservation is made and approved from guest, we collect 13.5% of commission fee from total amount of reservation.<br /><br /> 13.5% include the “Guiding you” commission fee, also fee of settlement of credit card.</p>\n<hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','merit'),
('13','2','ガイドになる理由','Guiding You（ガイディングユー）でガイドになる理由と利益','ガイド,理由,アクティビティ,旅行,利益','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">ガイドになるメリットは？</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_1_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"what\'s guiding you\" width=\"1170\" height=\"700\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_pic_margin_top\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<p><br /><br /> Guiding you でガイドになるメリットはなに？<br /><br /> それは沢山あります！<br /><br /><br /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>空いている時間で利益を生む</li>\n</ul><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_2_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /><p>アナタの語学・知識・趣味を生かして世界中の観光客を案内する事で収入が得られます<br /><br /> 無料で広告を載せ、世界中から集客ができます</p>\n<hr /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>世界各国に友人を作る</li>\n</ul><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_3_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /><p>世界中の方にアナタの国や町を紹介しましょう！<br />好きになってもらえるチャンスです<br /><br /> 世界中の方々と友達になれるチャンスです</p>\n<hr /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_space_1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>掲載は無料</li>\n</ul><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_4_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /><p>Guiding youにガイドやアクティビティを掲載するのは無料です</p>\n<hr /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-push-1 cms_space_1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\">\n<ul class=\"list-1\"><li><em class=\"icon-ok\"></em>個人情報も安心</li>\n</ul><img title=\"cms-img\" src=\"http://guiding-you.co//img/cms/merit_5_compressed.jpg\" alt=\"cms-img\" width=\"100%\" /><p>個人を特定する住所は最後まで公開されない