('16','1','Member  Legal Notice','Member  Legal Notice of Guiding You','legal notice','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">“Guiding You” Member’s Usage Agreement</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><br /><p><br /> This is the agreement that “Guiding you limited” provide for the service.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">1.Term’s definition</h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><th width=\"30%\">\n<p>Member</p>\n</th>\n<td width=\"70%\">\n<p>All of users registered the “Guiding you”</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><th>\n<p>Guest</p>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p>Guest who made a reservation at the member of “guiding you”.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><th>\n<p>Guide</p>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p>Company, organization and individual that register as member of “Guiding you” and registered for guide service and activity service.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><th>\n<p>Activity</p>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p>Activity that posted when registered as guide.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><th>\n<p>Service</p>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p>General term of activity and guide that the guide provides.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><th>\n<p>Terms</p>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p>General terms of rules that “Guiding-you” defines.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><th>\n<p>Deal</p>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p>Appointment that occur in “Guiding you”.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><th>\n<p>Membership information</p>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p>general terms of the personal information that you registered your personal information when you registered as a member/host of “Guiding you”.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><th>\n<p>Guide Information</p>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p>The information for the guide that registered as guide.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><th>\n<p>Activity Information</p>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p>The information of activities that registered.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><th>\n<p>The site</p>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p>“The site” is the website/app of “Guiding you”.</p>\n</td>\n</tr></tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">2.Member’s Definition</h2>\n<p><br /> The member is able to use the site, based on the rules that “Guiding you limited” defined. The member is able to make an appointment of the guide, also you are able to provide the guide service/activity once registered as a guide, to experience for guest members.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">3.Member Registration</h2>\n<p><br /> Anyone can register as a member nationality, age, gender are just matter of languages.<br /> Just write down your precise information when register. When needs of changing of information, change quick through “my account”</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">4.Making the reservation</h2>\n<p><br /> Member can make a reservation, check out the services, activities and guides that is posted on the website.<br /> If you are under 18 years old and wants to make a reservation, you have to get agreement from your guardian.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">5.Settlement of payment of service</h2>\n<p><br /> You have to establish the PayPal account, you can make a payment with your credit card, and however you will be creating the PayPal account when you are paying on credit card automatically.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">6.Canceling of Reservation</h2>\n<p><br /> You can cancel the service after the reservation. Canceling before 48 hours of the date of the event, we will return 100% of the reservation fee, But canceling within 48 hours of the date of the event,(Cou