ol-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">10.Disclaimer</h2>\n<p><br /> We are not responsible for the damage that occur to guest and guide through any kinds of computer accidents such as delay of communication, extinction of the date, and illegal access by the hacker.<br /><br /> We are not responsible for the damage that causes stopping the service may occur through the natural disaster, war, terrorism, maintenance etc… <br /><br /> We will watch that virus does not contain in domain, server and webpage, however we can not promise that we can not be sure 100% that virus will not be contained.<br /><br /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">11.Stops the service and delete of membership.</h2>\n<p><br /> In the case the guide violate the agreement of this site; we will delete the membership without the notice by the content.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">12.Changes of service</h2>\n<p><br /> We are able to change or vanish the content partly of service by our decision.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">13.Changes of regulations</h2>\n<p><br /> We are able to change, vanish or add the agreement by our decision.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">14.Resign</h2>\n<p><br /> Your personal information will be deleted, once resigned.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','member-legal-notice'),
