('18','1','FAQ','FAQ for Guiding You','FAQ,guide,activity,guiding you','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">FAQ</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">1.Is it free to register to be a member?</h2>\n<p><br /> Yes, Anyone can register for free to be a member. However, if you want to register to be a guide, you must be over 18 years old.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">2.What is the difference between registering as a guide and activity?</h2>\n<p><br /> The type of service you provide is different, one is serving as a guide and takes tourists and introduces your city, and another one is providing tourists fun activities such as sport events etc...</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">3.Why do I need a PayPal account, in order to register and settlement for the reservation?</h2>\n<p><br /> Everyone who uses “Guiding you” will need PayPal account, also person who do not have PayPal accounts can reserve the service by using the credit card. The PayPal account will be established when you pay by using the credit card.<br /><br /> We unified by using the PayPal account because of the costs of transfer and convenience for the payment of reservation of guide.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">4.Is there a commission fees?</h2>\n<p><br /> There is no commission fee to make a reservation for the guest. <br /> Once reservation is made and approved from guest, we collect 13.5% of commission fee from total amount of reservation from guide.<br /><span style=\"font-size:90%;\">※Please check PayPal web site for their charge </span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">5.Can I cancel after the reservation?</h2>\n<p><br /> Yes, you can cancel after the reservation.<br /> We will return 100% of reservation fee before the 48 hours of the date on which the event is to take place.<br /> Canceling within 48 hours of the date on which the event is to take place (Counting from 24:00 O’clock of the place that event is happening) occur 50% of canceling fee.<br /><br /> Canceling the date on which the event is to take place, 100% of canceling fee occurs.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">6.When the payment of guide and activity will be transferred?</h2>\n<p><br /> The payment will be transferred to your PayPal account within 3days from 1dayafter the date on which the event is to take place.<br /> We temporally hold the payment that settled from the guide during we receive the money from the guest.<br /> It is possible the payment will be delayed if the guest contacts for trouble that is happened during the activity and guide, in order to make sure.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">7.Can the guide cancel the guest’s reservation?</h2>\n<p><br /> If the plan has got changes, please tell the guest and us before the 48 hours of the date on which the event is to take place.<br /> There is no penalty for the guide in this case.<br /> However, canceling within 48 hours of the date of which the event is to take place, there will penalty occur except the reason that is unavoidable of canceling.<br /> (Please check the agreement if the reason of canceling applies.)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">8.There is no region and country where I registered as a guide…</h2>\n<p><br /> Please inform us through the contact, we will consider of adding new region and country.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">9.I could not meet my guide on the date I suppose to meet for the reservation…</h2>\n<p><br /> Please contact us as soon as possible for the sake guide faced with some kinds of reason to not meet you or any kinds of troubles that occur.<br /><br /><a href=\"mailto:trouble@guiding-you.co\">trouble@guiding-you.co</a><br /><br /> In the case, we will return all of reservation fees if the guide has not accomplish his responsibility.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">10.How can I register the guide service and activity service?</h2>\n<p><br /> First of all, please finish registering and become a member, and then, register as a guide at the “my account” page. <br /> You can register, add, change, and delete your guide service and activity service by following <br /> “My account”→ “my guide account”→ “Activity”.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">11.Can register multiple guide and activities.</h2>\n<p><br /> Yes, you can register multiple guide services and activity services.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">12.What is GuideBlog?</h2>\n<p><br /> It is a tool to inform your registered guide course of content and recent conditions attractively.<br /> Any other information is good, as long as the guest can refer your information.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','faq'),
('18','2','FAQ','Guiding You（ガイディングユー）のFAQ','FAQ,ガイディングユー','<h1 class=\"page-heading bottom-indent\">FAQ</h1>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">1.会員登録は無料ですか？</h2>\n<p><br /> はい、誰でも無料で会員登録できます<br /> ただしサービスを提供する側のガイド登録は18歳以上の方と限定しています</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">2.ガイドとアクティビティ登録の違いはなんですか？</h2>\n<p><br /> アナタが提供するサービスはガイドサービスかアクティビティのサービスかの違いです<br /><br /> ガイドサービスはガイドがゲストを名所に連れて行き観光をするのがガイドで、アクティビティは何らかのイベントやスポーツ等に参加する場合に使います</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">3.ガイド登録や予約決済に何故Paypal口座が必要ですか？</h2>\n<p><br /> Guiding youを利用する方は全員paypal口座が必要となりますが、現在ペイパル口座が無い方でもクレジットカードがあればその場でサービスの予約は出来ます。<br /> クレジットで支払う時に同時にペイパルの口座が作成される仕組みです。<br /><br /> 世界中でガイドの予約とガイドの登録が出来るため、ガイドの予約料金の振込コストと利便性を考えてpaypal口座で統一させて頂きました。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">4.手数料は掛かりますか？</h2>\n<p><br /> ゲストは予約に手数料は掛かりません<br /> ガイドはゲストからの予約金額の13.5％をクレジットの決済料と弊社手数料として徴収されます<br /><span style=\"font-size:90%;\">※ペイパルの利用手数料はペイパルサイトでご確認ください</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">5.予約後のキャンセルはできますか？</h2>\n<p><br /> 予約後のキャンセルは可能です<br /> 実施日の48時間前なら予約金100%を返金しますが、実施日の48時間以内（現地時間午前0時起算）にキャンセルした場合は50%のキャンセル料金が発生します<br /><br /> 実施当日のキャンセルは100%のキャンセル料金が発生します</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">6.ガイドやアクティビティの代金は何時振り込まれますか？</h2>\n<p><br /> 実施日の翌日から起算して3営業日以内にガイドが登録したpaypal口座に振り込まれます<br /> それ迄の間ガイドから決済された料金は当社が一時預かります<br /> ただし、ゲストからトラブルコンタクトがあった場合は、内容を確認するため振込日は遅れる場合があります</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">7.ガイドがゲストの予約をキャンセルできますか？</h2>\n<p><br /> 予定が変更した場合、実施日の48時間以上前にゲスト及び当社にお知らせ下さい、この場合ガイドにペナルティーはありません<br /><br /> ただし、実施日48時間以内のキャンセルは、回避出来ない理由を除いてペナルティーが発生します（回避出来ない理由は利用規約を確認ください）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">8.ガイドとして登録した国や地域が無いのですが</h2>\n<p><br /> コンタクトでお問い合わせ頂ければ希望の国や地域の追加を検討します</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">9.予約当日にガイドと出会えなかったのですが</h2>\n<p><br /> ガイドが急用で待ち合わせ場所に来れなかった或は何らか問題が発生した場合は至急当社のトラブルコンタクトに連絡ください<br /><br /><a href=\"mailto:trouble@guiding-you.co\">trouble@guiding-you.co</a><br /><br /> ガイドが責務を果たさなかった場合は予約代金を返金します</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">10.どうやってガイドサービスやアクティビティサービスを登録するのですか？</h2>\n<p><br /> 先ずは会員登録してからmy accountページ内でガイド登録を済ませて下さい<br /> My account　→　my guide account　→　activities　であなたのガイドサービスやアクティビティサービスの登録、追加、変更、削除ができます</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">11.ガイドとアクティビティは複数登録できますか？</h2>\n<p><br /> はい、ガイドサービスとアクティビティサービスは複数登録できます</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1 cms_sentence\">\n<div class=\"cms-box\"><br /><h2 class=\"align_left\">12.ガイドブログはなんですか？</h2>\n<p><br /> アナタが登録したガイドコースの近況やアクティビティの内容や近況をゲストに魅力的に伝えるツールです。<br /> その他の情報でもゲストが参考となる情報であれば何でも結構です。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','faq'),
